{"tid":1851846,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉建源：政府應該在疫情消除後才復課","createTime":"2020-01-30T07:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:11:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"088ca883553f62d0dc658a8d2ecba8b17c748b96","tid":1851846,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:44:12.000Z","msg":"立法會衞生事務委員會召開特別會議，討論本港預防及控制新型冠狀病毒的措施。<br />\n<br />\n在會後，委員會副主席陳凱欣形容，政府抗疫工作反應慢、決定遲、判斷錯。她建議當局將7間聯網指定診所改為普通診症，對全球旅客要求健康申報，落區宣傳清潔工作，嚴防社區爆發。<br />\n<br />\n教育界議員葉建源說，政府應該在疫情消除後才復課。而復課前，政府要妥善制定內地過年返港學童的應對措施、學校預防設施等問題，否則擔心學校會成為傳播風險極高的地方。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505661-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505661-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rFSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=e5294e38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505661-20200130.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=efea4c31\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505661-20200130.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a9f11d4bf568717455c09ac58ac2f8cca59d098a","tid":1851846,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"in other words, 政府突然話復課係咪代表佢地已經控制到疫情？"},{"pid":"de467f361c41a4b8a491989fbb514e87746e26be","tid":1851846,"uid":93383,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"仲話2月17復課<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n疫情高峰期幾時呀 同你講又唔聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118aaf69ddeb0494fcb2877c2cad569186cc1563","tid":1851846,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"無了期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a